      },
      {
        "segment": "Could you tell me the nature of that harsh toll and why it would be experienced?",
        "start_offset": 174,
        "end_offset": 254,
        "start": 14.8,
        "end": 21.22
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 255,
        "end_offset": 263,
        "start": 21.24,
        "end": 21.62
      },
      {
        "segment": "The physical energy level is a measure of the amount of available energy of the body complex of a mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 264,
        "end_offset": 387,
        "start": 25.241,
        "end": 66.142
      },
      {
        "segment": "The vital energy measurement is one which expresses the amount of energy of being of the mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 388,
        "end_offset": 502,
        "start": 68.602,
        "end": 109.103
      },
      {
        "segment": "This entity has great distortions in the direction of mind complex activity, spirit complex activity, and that great conduit to the Creator, the will.",
        "start_offset": 503,
        "end_offset": 653,
        "start": 111.403,
        "end": 163.784
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, this instrument's vital energy, even in the absence of any physical reserve measurable, is quite substantial.",
        "start_offset": 654,
        "end_offset": 774,
        "start": 167.704,
        "end": 204.305
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, the use of this energy of will, mind, and spirit for the things of the physical complex causes a far greater distortion in the lessening of the vital energy than would the use of this energy for those things which are in the deepest desires and will of the mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 775,
        "end_offset": 1066,
        "start": 206.885,
        "end": 304.827
      },
      {
        "segment": "In this entity these desires are for service to the Creator.",
        "start_offset": 1067,
        "end_offset": 1127,
        "start": 307.167,
        "end": 323.447
      },
      {
        "segment": "This entity sees all service as service to the Creator and this is why we have cautioned the support group and the instrument itself in this regard.",
        "start_offset": 1128,
        "end_offset": 1276,
        "start": 327.408,
        "end": 372.209
      },
      {
        "segment": "All services are not equal in depth of distortion.",
        "start_offset": 1277,
        "end_offset": 1327,
        "start": 373.929,
        "end": 390.269
      },
      {
        "segment": "The over-use of this vital energy is, to be literal, the rapid removal of life force.",
        "start_offset": 1328,
